---
// src/components/RankBadge.astro
// 五階位階徽記 — 母題沿用官網 Logo 的「兩圓交集」，隨位階逐步顯影。
// 用 currentColor（= --brand-strong）畫線，交集以 --accent 填色。
interface Props {
  rank: 'value-object' | 'entity' | 'aggregate-root' | 'bounded-context' | 'domain-expert';
  size?: number;
}
const { rank, size = 60 } = Astro.props;
const RING = { fill: 'none', stroke: 'currentColor', 'stroke-width': '2.2' };
---
<svg
  width={size}
  height={size}
  viewBox="0 0 100 100"
  style="display:block; color: var(--brand-strong);"
  role="img"
  aria-label={rank}
>
  {rank === 'value-object' && (
    <>
      <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="22" {...RING} opacity="0.55" />
      <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="4.5" fill="var(--accent)" />
    </>
  )}
  {rank === 'entity' && (
    <>
      <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="22" {...RING} />
      <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="11" {...RING} opacity="0.7" />
      <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="3.4" fill="var(--accent)" />
    </>
  )}
  {rank === 'aggregate-root' && (
    <>
      <circle cx="38" cy="50" r="22" {...RING} />
      <circle cx="62" cy="50" r="22" {...RING} />
      <path d="M50 30 A22 22 0 0 1 50 70 A22 22 0 0 1 50 30 Z" fill="var(--accent)" />
    </>
  )}
  {rank === 'bounded-context' && (
    <>
      <rect x="10" y="18" width="80" height="64" rx="10" {...RING} opacity="0.5" />
      <circle cx="38" cy="50" r="19" {...RING} />
      <circle cx="62" cy="50" r="19" {...RING} />
      <path d="M50 33.7 A19 19 0 0 1 50 66.3 A19 19 0 0 1 50 33.7 Z" fill="var(--accent)" />
    </>
  )}
  {rank === 'domain-expert' && (
    <>
      <path d="M22 30 Q50 10 78 30" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" />
      <circle cx="38" cy="54" r="19" {...RING} />
      <circle cx="62" cy="54" r="19" {...RING} />
      <path d="M50 37.7 A19 19 0 0 1 50 70.3 A19 19 0 0 1 50 37.7 Z" fill="var(--accent)" />
      <g stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.8">
        <path d="M50 78 v8" /><path d="M28 74 l-4 6" /><path d="M72 74 l4 6" />
      </g>
    </>
  )}
</svg>
